          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10098,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1009801,
            "DisplayOrder": 660,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12200,
            "LocalizeKR": "에이에이, 이런 아저씨랑\n같이 있어 봤자\n뭐가 재밌다구.",
            "LocalizeJP": "またまたぁ～こんな\nおじさんといたって、\n別に楽しくないでしょ～",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10098,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1009801,
            "DisplayOrder": 670,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5650,
            "LocalizeKR": "으, 으헤에~. 그 설정,\n계속 가는 것이려나…",
            "LocalizeJP": "う、うへぇ～…\nその設定、まだやるの…？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10098,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1009801,
            "DisplayOrder": 680,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11000,
            "LocalizeKR": "아저씨는 조금\n부담스러울지도~.",
            "LocalizeJP": "おじさんにはちょっと\n荷が重いかも～",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10098,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1009801,
            "DisplayOrder": 690,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9050,
            "LocalizeKR": "…뭐어, 선생이 사이드킥을\n하고 싶다면 맞춰주지\n못 할 것도 없지만.",
            "LocalizeJP": "…まあ、先生が相棒役を\n買って出てくれるのなら、\n合わせるけどさぁ。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
